Walt Disney's The Nature of Things

description: There are mysteries in this world which cannot be explained by modern science. There are creatures without origin, actions without causation. And then, there is Jonny Quest! Son of globe-trotting phenomenologist Dr. Benton Quest, Jonny faces extraordinary challenges in exotic locales. He travels the world with his father and his investigative team -- Roger "Race" Bannon, his daughter Jessie, Hadji, and Bandit -- and though he doesn't always find answers, he never fails to find danger!
name: Net Of Chaos (Part 1)

volume.name: The Real Adventures Of Jonny Quest

name: Hawkeye and the Last of the Mohicans

description: As the kids navigate their way through a flattened and flooded New York, they discover human survivors of the apocalypse — who want superhuman blood! Can a desperate plan bail them out, or will the kids serve the ultimate sentence for being post-humans? Plus: Part 3 of the Wetworks backup story by Gage and Badeaux!
name: Teenage Wasteland, Part 2 - Hell Of A Town

description: Jonny's faced danger a million times, in more ways than your average teen can imagine. But this time is different, as the QuestTeam heads to Budapest to face a ring of young computer hackers and a strange gypsy rumored to be a vampire! But the real adventure doesn't end there. When Bandit goes missing, Jonny has a hunch that real danger is in his future!
name: Net Of Chaos (Part 2)

volume.name: The Real Adventures Of Jonny Quest
